		{"id":"emergence_core","type":"group","x":1000,"y":-800,"width":1000,"height":400,"color":"3","label":"涌现维度 🌀"},
		{"id":"ai_1","type":"text","text":"# AGI 之路\n\n```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    A[深度学习] --> B[强化学习]\n    B --> C[元学习]\n    C --> D[通用智能]\n    D --> E[超级智能]\n```\n\n**关键挑战**\n- 符号接地问题\n- 常识推理\n- 意识模拟","x":2050,"y":250,"width":700,"height":300,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ai_2","type":"link","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2303.12712","x":2100,"y":600,"width":600,"height":150},
		{"id":"consciousness_1","type":"text","text":"# 意识的涌现\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    A[神经元] --> B[神经网络]\n    B --> C[认知模块]\n    C --> D[自我意识]\n    D --> E[超验体验]\n```\n\n**整合信息理论 (IIT)**\n- Φ值测量\n- 意识的数学模型","x":1050,"y":-250,"width":350,"height":300,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"note_math_reality","type":"text","text":"## 数学的本体地位\n\n数学是发现还是发明？\n- 柏拉图主义\n- 形式主义\n- 直觉主义","x":-500,"y":400,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"note_quantum_philosophy","type":"text","text":"## 量子-哲学桥梁\n\n观察者效应与主观唯心主义的相似性：\n- 意识创造现实？\n- 多重宇宙与可能世界","x":-300,"y":200,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"singularity","type":"text","text":"# 🌟 奇点\n\n所有维度的交汇点\n\n**技术奇点**\n**意识奇点**\n**知识奇点**\n\n$$\\lim_{t \\to \\infty} \\frac{dI}{dt} = \\infty$$","x":900,"y":300,"width":400,"height":300,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"consciousness_2","type":"text","text":"# 自由意志悖论\n\n> \"我思故我在\" - 笛卡尔\n\n1. 决定论 vs 自由意志\n2. 李贝特实验\n3. 量子意识理论","x":1450,"y":-200,"width":350,"height":250,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"consciousness_3","type":"link","url":"https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/consciousness/","x":1250,"y":100,"width":400,"height":200},
		{"id":"time_dimension","type":"text","text":"# ⏰ 时间本质\n\n- 块宇宙理论\n- 因果循环\n- 时间之箭\n\n过去、现在、未来同时存在？","x":1400,"y":500,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"philosophy_1","type":"text","text":"# 本体论问题\n\n## 存在的本质\n- 柏拉图的理念论\n- 亚里士多德的实体论\n- 海德格尔的此在\n\n> \"存在先于本质\" - 萨特","x":-150,"y":750,"width":350,"height":400,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"note_ai_consciousness","type":"text","text":"## AI 意识猜想\n\n机器能否产生真正的意识？\n- 中文房间论证\n- 功能主义观点\n- 涌现主义解释","x":1600,"y":400,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"quantum_1","type":"text","text":"# 量子纠缠\n\n$$|\\psi\\rangle = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}}(|00\\rangle + |11\\rangle)$$\n\n- EPR悖论\n- 贝尔不等式\n- 量子隐形传态","x":50,"y":50,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"quantum_3","type":"file","file":"量子计算基础.md","x":200,"y":300,"width":400,"height":250},
		{"id":"philosophy_2","type":"text","text":"# 认识论危机\n\n**如何确定知识的真实性？**\n\n1. 经验主义 vs 理性主义\n2. 怀疑论挑战\n3. 后现代解构","x":250,"y":800,"width":300,"height":300,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"quantum_2","type":"text","text":"# 波函数坍缩\n\n$$\\hat{H}|\\psi\\rangle = E|\\psi\\rangle$$\n\n观察者效应的哲学意义","x":400,"y":100,"width":300,"height":150,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"philosophy_3","type":"file","file":"东西方哲学对比.md","x":600,"y":750,"width":350,"height":400},
		{"id":"infinity_paradox","type":"text","text":"# ∞ 无限悖论\n\n**希尔伯特旅馆**\n**康托尔对角线**\n**芝诺悖论**\n\n$$\\aleph_0 < 2^{\\aleph_0} = \\aleph_1$$","x":200,"y":-400,"width":250,"height":250,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"math_1","type":"text","text":"# 哥德尔不完备定理\n\n**第一不完备定理**\n任何包含皮亚诺算术的一致形式系统都是不完备的\n\n**第二不完备定理**\n系统无法证明自身的一致性\n\n$$\\vdash_{PA} \\text{Con}(PA) \\rightarrow \\perp$$","x":-496,"y":-805,"width":600,"height":300,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"math_2","type":"text","text":"# 分形几何\n\n```python\ndef mandelbrot(c, max_iter=100):\n    z = 0\n    for n in range(max_iter):\n        if abs(z) > 2:\n            return n\n        z = z*z + c\n    return max_iter\n```\n\n自相似性与无限复杂度","x":-446,"y":-455,"width":500,"height":350,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"emergence_1","type":"text","text":"# 复杂系统涌现\n\n$$\\text{整体} > \\sum\\text{部分}$$\n\n- 蚁群智能\n- 大脑意识\n- 市场经济\n- 生命起源","x":1050,"y":-750,"width":400,"height":300,"color":"1"},
